before_action :set_{clipboard}, only: [:show, :edit, :update, :destroy]



private
    def set_{clipboard}
      @{clipboard} = {clipboard}.find(params[:id])
    end

    def {clipboard}_params
      params.require(:{clipboard}).permit(:first_name, :last_name, :want, :profile_image, :remote_profile_image_url)
    end
alfredsnippet.name: controller strong params
